<DOCNO>WT18-B15-7</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000233-B027-271</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://emernet.emergency.com:80/devlresp.htm 205.243.133.2 19970107233109 text/html 14640
HTTP/1.0 200 OK: Retrieving file
Server: Worldgroup/2.00 ICO/2.0
Date: Tue, 07 Jan 1997 23:24:42 GMT
