<br>
Several reports have surfaced that the Saudis have detained as many as forty (40) &quot;shi'ites radIcals&quot; and &quot;Saudi nationalists&quot; 
during their investigations, and that some of the suspects may have links to Iran or other Mid-Eastern countries. Secretary 
