<DOCNO>WT18-B15-16</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000233-B028-78</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://emernet.emergency.com:80/wmd-terr.htm 205.243.133.2 19970107233304 text/html 14356
HTTP/1.0 200 OK: Retrieving file
Server: Worldgroup/2.00 ICO/2.0
Date: Tue, 07 Jan 1997 23:26:38 GMT
Content-Length: 14156
Last-Modified: Tue, 07 Jan 1997 23:26:38 GMT
