<DOCNO>WT18-B15-61</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000233-B030-261</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://emernet.emergency.com:80/tersuspc.htm 205.243.133.2 19970107234221 text/html 12628
HTTP/1.0 200 OK: Retrieving file
Server: Worldgroup/2.00 ICO/2.0
Date: Tue, 07 Jan 1997 23:35:54 GMT
