<p><strong>ABOUT THE AUTHOR: </strong></p>
<p>Clark Staten is a veteran emergency services manager, having served more than 18 years with a major metropolitan 
fire department. He is the author of &quot;The Emergency Response Guide to Terrorism&quot; and is the Executive Director of 
the Emergency Response &amp; Research Institute, an emergency service 'think tank', based in Chicago, IL</p>
