<H3> U.S. DISASTER MANAGEMENT ORGANIZATIONS</H3>
<P>
The following list is a directory of information sources compiled by the
Natural Hazards Research and Applications Information Center staff. The
directory is divided into three sections: U.S. Domestic Organizations,
Academic Institutions,and Government Agencies.
<P> 

For further information contact:hazards@vaxf.colorado.edu
<P>

