<body>
<p>EmergencyNet News Brief<br>
07/19/96 - 13:22 CDT<br>
<br>
<font color="#FF0000"><font size=5><strong>FBI Announces Toll-Free Number For Flt. 800 Information</strong></font></font><br>
<br>
Spokesperson Jim Kallstrom from the New York City FBI Joint Terrorism Task-Force today announced that they 
are actively seeking asistance from citizens with any information regarding the crash/explosion of TWA Flt. 800. 
Kallstrom requested that anyone with specific information about the disaster, and particularly citizens of the Long 
Island, NY area, please call: <font color="#FF0000"><font size=4>888-245-4636</font></font>. E-mail can be sent to: <font color="#FF0000"><font size=4>newyork@fbi.gov</font></font><br>
