<TITLE>Chicago-FLASH; Multiple People Shot</TITLE>
<!-- Comment Here -->
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<B>** ENN NEWS FLASH **</B>
<BR>
EmergencyNet NEWS Service
<BR> 
Wednesday, December 6, 1995 - 1800 CST
<P>
Four people were shot in the alley behind 1716 West 61st Street in the 7th Police District on Chicago's South Side.  The possible gang-related shooting happened at about 1730 CST.  CPD units on the scene reported that none of the victims sustained life-threatening wounds.  The Chicago Fire Department responded to the incident with four ambulances.
<P>
Further details are being investigated by 7th District Tactical Units and Gangcrimes officers at the time of this report.
<P>
