<DOCNO>WT18-B15-291</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000233-B046-218</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://emernet.emergency.com:80/bombstry.htm 205.243.133.2 19970108002741 text/html 6414
HTTP/1.0 200 OK: Retrieving file
