<DOCNO>WT18-B15-296</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000233-B047-46</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://emernet.emergency.com:80/aolgold.htm 205.243.133.2 19970108002836 text/html 11928
HTTP/1.0 200 OK: Retrieving file
Server: Worldgroup/2.00 ICO/2.0
